Remember the brief that you provided to me above. Considering your brief, write the content plan for the following article:

'Title: Post-construction Stage: Assessing the Impact of Price Increases on Property Value
Explanation: This article will explore the effect of price increases on the overall value of the completed property, including potential impacts on resale value and long-term return on investment. It will offer suggestions for maximizing property value despite increased construction costs."
